headline: Agoda and Artotel Group Launch Dedicated Flagship Store to Capitalize on Intra-Asia Travel Momentum
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda is expanding its Flagship Store initiative with the launch of Artotel Group's first branded flagship store. This dedicated digital storefront enhances brand visibility and global marketing opportunities for Artotel Group, the leading Indonesian hospitality company, while providing travelers easy discovery to over 100 properties across Indonesia.

headline: Booking Holdings Split Highlights Push Into Media And AI Support
summary: Booking Holdings (NasdaqGS:BKNG) announces a 25-for-1 stock split, aiming to lower the trading price per share and increase accessibility for a wider range of investors.
